    "en": {
      "name": "Earthbound Immortal Red Nova",
      "effect": "There can only be 1 \"Earthbound Immortal\" monster on the field. During the Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can banish this card from your hand or GY; send 1 \"Earthbound Immortal\" monster or \"Red Dragon Archfiend\" from your hand or face-up Monster Zone to the GY, then you can apply 1 of these effects.\n\u25cf Special Summon 1 \"Earthbound\" monster from your Deck or Extra Deck.\n\u25cf Special Summon 1 \"Red Nova Dragon\" from your Extra Deck. (This is treated as a Synchro Summon.)\nYou can only use this effect of \"Earthbound Immortal Red Nova\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
